The 2023 JUNO Awards are coming to Edmonton, and you can win tickets!

 

Come along with me to Shades of Grey to shop for the JUNOS. Next stop is cocktails at the Confederation Lounge, and then head to La Cité Francophone for a Road to the JUNOS show.

 

Enter to WIN a one-night stay at Fairmont Hotel Macdonald, a $100 gift card for dinner downtown, and two tickets to The JUNO Awards on March 13 at Rogers Place.

 

To enter:

🎵 Follow me & @ExploreEdmonton.
🎵 Tag a friend you’d like to take to the JUNOS!

Contest rules:

Must be 18 years or older to enter. Winner must live in Canada. Giveaway is in no way sponsored, endorsed or administered by Instagram. Giveaway closes at 11:59PM on March 9, 2023. 

Winner will be contacted on March 10. Good Luck!

Love my summer cocktails refreshing and full of collagen. @aphina.co has the best wellness products and I chose the passion fruit collagen supplement to create a peach yuzu spritz. Full recipe coming tomorrow!##AphinaGlow #ad

The @aphina.co peach yuzu spritz 🍹
	⁃	1 oz lemongrass simple syrup (add lemongrass to 1 part sugar 1 part water and boil)
	⁃	1/4 cup muddled peaches and 4 sprigs of mint
	⁃	2 oz lime juice 
	⁃	1 oz alphina passion fruit collagen supplement 
	⁃	Top with regular or yuzu soda 
	⁃	Garnish with a cucumber ribbon
